{"tid":1872480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"天生冇安全感真係好難有幸福","createTime":"2020-02-10T06:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T14:42:28.000Z","uid":105891,"like":99,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5d4331e61a6c02e0079e223230bfcfc6ad50bb","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"當你愛/信任既人唔係你身邊，即使只係幾個鐘頭，你個心都有一種不安既感覺，會好期待佢幾時返。如果佢冇聽電話，你又會諗發生左咩事?係咪佢嬲左自己呢? 以上無限loop，永無止境.....而對方亦開始覺得煩，開始疏遠你。雖然知有時係自己諗多左，但控制唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以天生冇安全感既人真係好難有幸福，有冇人明白我?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7392f3e6a5aae009c78b9972336a592494cdc4f5","tid":1872480,"uid":231583,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"自己個世界唔可以全然圍住一個人轉，咁太危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛同信任下自己多d先啦"},{"pid":"ba8de43d1157cf320581a142d1fd6f82f3b712c5","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"我明 因為我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己畀多啲空間同興趣比自己先<br />\n鍾意一個人唔代表要成日圍住佢轉<br />\n唔係你會好似我咁後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722b467586df09425695cfead1042dcde058a2f0","tid":1872480,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"天生有病都係要醫嘅"},{"pid":"f8cc78b146e8281988cd394624cb9770a622af27","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7392f3e6a5aae009c78b9972336a592494cdc4f5","tid":1872480,"uid":231583,"like":24,"dislike":1