,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3051243c35d2d5021c93680b57f1c14996ab8ebc","tid":1872480,"uid":278349,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"我係咁諗，<br />\n一個想幸福嘅人，也必須是能夠讓人幸福的人，先有資格獲得幸福吧，但你咁樣對方又點會覺得幸福呢？<br />\n愛自己多d，令自己變到更加好。<br />\n利申曾經都好似樓豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc73ca7305013698ab14334f575c558e3ee6b4da","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90388fc0447f6e16d257c17930e8bdb7c8654ff0","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"722b467586df09425695cfead1042dcde058a2f0","tid":1872480,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"天生有病都係要醫嘅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"點醫呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"我靠睇書同做心理輔導<br />\n睇書係認清自己屬於邊種冇安全感 同埋知自己個行為模式<br />\n好快你開始明白好多擔心係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要做心理輔導係因為自己情緒真係影響到人<br />\n佢教你用冥想令自己不安冷靜落嚟先<br />\n同埋幫你探討你冇安全感嘅原因喺邊 再一齊諗點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400dd58718319de3768efa17ff6a0a564abacb16","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3051243c35d2d5021c93680b57f1c14996ab8ebc","tid":1872480,"uid":278349,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"我係咁諗，<br />\n一個想幸福嘅人，也必須是能夠讓人幸福的人，先有資格獲得幸福吧，但你咁樣對方又點會覺得幸福呢？<br />\n愛自己多d，令自己變到更加好。<br />\n利申曾經都好似樓豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"可能以前俾人背叛過，我當時對對方好好，點知到頭來一切係謊言。所以令人幸福不等於自己會有幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能因為咁，個心結未解開，好驚另一次既背叛。諗唔到點解開個結"},{"pid":"f166ab726c79a3e97c9bcb7531003b7fc89e06ac","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc73ca7305013698ab14334f575c558e3ee6b4da","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90388fc0447f6e16d257c17930e8bdb7c8654ff0","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"722b467586df09425695cfead1042dcde058a2f0","tid":1872480,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"天生有病都係要醫嘅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"點醫呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"我靠睇書同做心理輔導<br />\n睇書係認清自己屬於邊種冇安全感 同埋知自己個行為模式<br />\n好快你開始明白好多擔心係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要做心理輔導係因為自己情緒真係影響到人<br />\n佢教你用冥想令自己不安冷靜落嚟先<br />\n同埋幫你探討你冇安全感嘅原因喺邊 再一齊諗點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"可唔可以俾D資料睇睇"},{"pid":"949da330e30c4134e0f2b9b96568eb56ec4957d4","tid":1872480,"uid":94537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8cc78b146e8281988cd394624cb9770a622af27","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7392f3e6a5aae009c78b9972336a592494cdc4f5","tid":1872480,"uid":231583,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"自己個世界唔可以全然圍住一個人轉，咁太危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛同信任下自己多d先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"太愛一個人就自然會將自己既心思放晒佢身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但一旦你同佢分手，就會好似世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"我之前諗過如果分咗手我一定會了結自己就算⋯<br />\n唔係唔想愛多啲自己同信任自己<br />\n係好驚當自己慢慢咁變好之後散咗<br />\n所有努力前功盡廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有變好同時都想對方比多啲愛我㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a445bc90b414a1eaa8369965d3f1eb704ab12f","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f166ab726c79a3e97c9bcb7531003b7fc89e06ac","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc73ca7305013698ab14334f575c558e3ee6b4da","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90388fc0447f6e16d257c17930e8bdb7c8654ff0","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"點醫呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"我靠睇書同做心理輔導<br />\n睇書係認清自己屬於邊種冇安全感 同埋知自己個行為模式<br />\n好快你開始明白好多擔心係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要做心理輔導係因為自己情緒真係影響到人<br />\n佢教你用冥想令自己不安冷靜落嚟先<br />\n同埋幫你探討你冇安全感嘅原因喺邊 再一齊諗點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"可唔可以俾D資料睇睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"睇書我係睇周慕姿嘅《關係黑洞》<br />\n台灣人寫嘅<br />\n佢幾全面分析冇安全感嘅人嘅行為模式<br />\n曾經被背叛都係其中一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好將受過嘅傷帶畀下一個度啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面位巴打講得好啱 要愛自己先愛到其他人<br />\n冇安全感就係唔識愛自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e20e616c3021c194829e7301891d0449d83782","tid":1872480,"uid":175783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"我都係 之前好嚴重 但而家好返好多<br />\nEX都係因為咁而離開我<br />\n現任好有耐性 一開頭都會好好陪住我 但有次迫到佢好大壓力忍無可忍嘅時候 佢提出想分手<br />\n我就知應該要醒 唔可以再咁落去 對人同對自己都辛苦 <br />\n唔想因為又咁樣而趕走男朋友 所以自己都開始試下做運動 做多左運動成個人都開心左 無咁容易亂諗野同埋對自己有自信左 (之前好多時亂諗野都係因為無自信覺得唔夠人靚男朋友會出軌)<br />\n而家段關係健康左好多 我又唔會成日亂諗野 佢又唔會因為我亂諗野而好大壓力"},{"pid":"ac44350f1cae977cc817b4d73dcda23361aa9217","tid":1872480,"uid":125966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb14aa6058ae46213fbd2bfe280bddbd06ae0ed0","tid":1872480,"uid":125966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"29a8249313f05d31e14cc24380c7b94a350dcfc4","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6a445bc90b414a1eaa8369965d3f1eb704ab12f","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f166ab726c79a3e97c9bcb7531003b7fc89e06ac","tid":1872480,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc73ca7305013698ab14334f575c558e3ee6b4da","tid":1872480,"uid":13391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"我靠睇書同做心理輔導<br />\n睇書係認清自己屬於邊種冇安全感 同埋知自己個行為模式<br />\n好快你開始明白好多擔心係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要做心理輔導係因為自己情緒真係影響到人<br />\n佢教你用冥想令自己不安冷靜落嚟先<br />\n同埋幫你探討你冇安全感嘅原因喺邊 再一齊諗點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"可唔可以俾D資料睇睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"睇書我係睇周慕姿嘅《關係黑洞》<br />\n台灣人寫嘅<br />\n佢幾全面分析冇安全感嘅人嘅行為模式<br />\n曾經被背叛都係其中一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好將受過嘅傷帶畀下一個度啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面位巴打講得好啱 要愛自己先愛到其他人<br />\n冇安全感就係唔識愛自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx"